n33\t\n34\t## Must Read Before Using\n35\t\n36\t- `bin/gsd-t.js` lines 4544-4561 (`verify-gate` dispatch case) — the exact\n37\t  spawnSync dispatcher pattern D1 must replicate at integrate.\n38\t- `bin/gsd-t.js` ~lines 1181-1185 and ~2480-2485 — global-bin propagation\n39\t  arrays the new module name must be added to at integrate.\n40\t- `bin/journey-coverage-cli.cjs` — exit-code convention (0/4/2) precedent.\n41\t- `.gsd-t/progress.md` M57 row — authoritative SC1 fixture spec (new `hooks/`\n42\t  dir committed, absent from Dockerfile COPY → `missing[]` non-empty + exit 4).\n43\t\n44\t## Dependencies\n45\t\n46\t- Depends on: nothing (file-disjoint from D2; parallel wave).\n47\t- Depended on by: integrate phase (verify.md wire-in + CLI dispatch), D2 shares\n48\t  only the integrate-sequenced files — no execute-time coupling.\n49\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_013TZF28A2StK6MConWNruRz","session_id":"58ad06dd-2644-4e21-9536-13779b8ab76f","uuid":"6a011258-8b72-4f00-a36c-b2eb3e380496","timestamp":"2026-05-18T21:39:45.293Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Execute M57 D1 build-coverage"}
