{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_014ezVtpUj2G7JsGVdmUhLUp","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Constraints: m57-d2-ci-command-parity\n2\t\n3\t## Must Follow\n4\t\n5\t- Zero external runtime deps — Node built-ins only. No YAML library: parse\n6\t  `cloudbuild.yaml` / `.github/workflows/*.yml` with a minimal line/regex scan\n7\t  sufficient for the `steps[].args` / `jobs[].steps[].run` fields. Document the\n8\t  parse approach's known limits in the contract.\n9\t- `.cjs` module, `'use strict';`, header docblock naming the contract (mirror\n10\t  `bin/gsd-t-verify-gate.cjs`).\n11\t- CLI entry self-invokes (`require.main === module`), `--json` output, exit **4**\n12\t  on `ok:false`, **0** on `ok:true`, **2** on usage error (match D1 / journey\n13\t  CLI convention for consistency).\n14\t- Detection precedence is LOCKED (cloudbuild → workflows → Dockerfile RUN →\n15\t  package.json scripts). Do not add heuristics, do not reorder, do not add an\n16\t  opt-in flag for docker. Presence of `Dockerfile` is the sole docker trigger.\n17\t- Cache clear is mandatory before running detected commands — failing to clear\n18\t  caches reintroduces the exact stale-cache blind spot M57 exists to close.\n19\t- Defensive: missing `docker` binary → record note + treat docker step as\n20\t  skipped-not-failed (so projects without Docker daemon don't hard-fail);\n21\t  missing all CI artifacts AND no package.json scripts → `ok:true` + note.\n22\t- Functions under 30 lines where practical; named helpers per detection source\n23\t  and for the cache-clear step.\n24\t\n25\t## Must Not\n26\t\n27\t- Modify any file outside Owned scope. `bin/gsd-t.js` and\n28\t  `commands/gsd-t-verify.md` are SHARED — integrate-sequenced only, never in\n29\t  the parallel execute wave (D1 also edits both).\n30\t- Import or copy code from the TimeTracking project (INSPECT-only — post-mortem\n31\t  facts in `.gsd-t/progress.md` M57 row define the planted-regression fixture).\n32\t- Add a new npm dependency or a YAML parser dep.\n33\t- Shell out without timeouts — every spawned command (incl. `docker build`)\n34\t  must have a bounded timeout and stream/capture output.\n35\t\n36\t## Must Read Before Using\n37\t\n38\t- `bin/gsd-t.js` lines 4544-4561 (`verify-gate` dispatch) — exact dispatcher\n39\t  pattern to replicate at integrate.\n40\t- `bin/gsd-t.js` ~lines 1181-1185 and ~2480-2485 — global-bin arrays.\n41\t- `.gsd-t/progress.md` M57 row — authoritative SC2 fixture spec (Dockerfile\n42\t  project, planted tsc strict regression a warm-cache local tsc misses, real\n43\t  `docker build` must fail → `ok:false`).\n44\t- `bin/gsd-t-verify-gate.cjs` Track 2 — how detected-command results are\n45\t  shaped/consumed downstream (read-only; informs envelope design for the\n46\t  verify.md wire-in at integrate).\n47\t\n48\t## Dependencies\n49\t\n50\t- Depends on: nothing (file-disjoint from D1; parallel wave).\n51\t- Depended on by: integrate phase (verify.md wire-in + CLI dispatch). No\n52\t  execute-time coupling with D1.\n53\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_0149nXxtttvom24BpCbenYek","session_id":"58ad06dd-2644-4e21-9536-13779b8ab76f","uuid":"8fa49411-668e-468b-adfe-ef2db8327184","timestamp":"2026-05-18T21:40:04.503Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Execute M57 D2 ci-parity"}
