{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01S1T9TLM1PdG9f237UfB7v4","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01JHzdtnDEFsAzBCrzR3jAMW","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/david/projects/GSD-T/.gsd-t/contracts/cli-build-coverage-contract.md","old_string":"## Defensive Behavior\n\n- No git repo / detached HEAD / identical refs → exit 2 with a clear message.\n- No CI artifacts at all → `ok:true`, `note:\"no CI artifacts detected\"`, exit 0\n  (nothing to be inconsistent with — this is not a failure).\n- Empty diff → `ok:true`, `newPaths:[]`, exit 0.","new_string":"## Defensive Behavior\n\n- No git repo / detached HEAD / identical refs → `UsageError` thrown (not\n  returned in envelope); CLI catches and exits 2 with a clear message.\n- No CI artifacts at all → `ok:true`, `note:\"no CI artifacts detected\"`, exit 0\n  (nothing to be inconsistent with — this is not a failure).\n- Empty diff → `ok:true`, `newPaths:[]`, `note:\"empty diff\"`, exit 0."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":765,"cache_read_input_tokens":50080,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":765,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":73,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_013TZF28A2StK6MConWNruRz","session_id":"58ad06dd-2644-4e21-9536-13779b8ab76f","uuid":"f7af61e1-4955-47bc-b5a1-7b5cb7137c04","request_id":"req_011CbAmKsfejsyuixtWJfUVR","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Execute M57 D1 build-coverage"}
