{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TBsNxEvXbz4H4zhWTJcgFG","type":"tool_result","content":"✔ SC1: new hooks/ dir not COPY'd → ok:false, missing includes \"hooks\", API (12.746958ms)\n✔ SC1: CLI subprocess exits 4 for docker-cloudbuild fixture with hooks/ uncovered (243.691458ms)\n✔ copy-dot: Dockerfile with COPY . . → ok:true (10.496667ms)\n✔ no-ci: no Dockerfile/cloudbuild/workflows → ok:true with note (9.913083ms)\n✔ no-ci fixture: CLI exits 0 (217.896334ms)\n✔ empty diff → ok:true, newPaths:[] (10.414708ms)\n✔ usage error (bad git ref) → exit 2 (167.050709ms)\n✔ usage error (not a git repo) → exit 2 (34.470416ms)\n✔ gha-only: workflow references src/ but not hooks/ → hooks in missing (9.776959ms)\n✔ checkBuildCoverage: src/ present in Dockerfile COPY → src not in missing (9.087458ms)\n✔ checkBuildCoverage: multiple uncovered paths all appear in missing[] (8.985708ms)\n✔ checkBuildCoverage: identical baseRef/headRef → throws UsageError (caught by CLI as exit 2) (156.519917ms)\n✔ checkBuildCoverage return shape has all required fields (10.408667ms)\nℹ tests 13\nℹ suites 0\nℹ pass 13\nℹ fail 0\nℹ cancelled 0\nℹ skipped 0\nℹ todo 0\nℹ duration_ms 934.601042","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_013TZF28A2StK6MConWNruRz","session_id":"58ad06dd-2644-4e21-9536-13779b8ab76f","uuid":"47d8196d-bb9d-4b61-8ba3-f21f21a68593","timestamp":"2026-05-18T21:44:33.235Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Execute M57 D1 build-coverage"}
