ence found between code and contract — all fields, detection order, cache paths, docker trigger, and exit codes match exactly. Flipped `Status: DRAFT → STABLE`, `Version: 0.1.0 → 1.0.0`.\n\n**`node --test test/m57-d2-ci-parity.test.js`**: 22 tests total — **21 pass, 1 skipped** (SC2 docker test; self-skipped with message \"No Docker daemon available\").\n\n**`npm test` full suite**: **2584 pass, 0 fail, 1 skipped** (2547 baseline + 38 new D2 tests). Zero regressions.\n\n**SC2 docker test**: Self-skipped with message `No Docker daemon available — SC2 docker-dependent assertion skipped. Detection+cache-clear path tested unconditionally below.` The unconditional sub-test `SC2_detection_and_cache_clear_unconditional` runs on all hosts and validates both detection and that `clearBuildCaches` removes the stale `.tsbuildinfo`.\n\n**Contract divergence reconciled**: None — code and contract were in alignment. The parse limits documented in the module docblock (inline-array cloudbuild args, first-job-only workflow steps, single-line Dockerfile RUN) match what the contract states."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a30538bbcbf9893b6 (use SendMessage with to: 'a30538bbcbf9893b6' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 63230\ntool_uses: 39\nduration_ms: 413903</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"58ad06dd-2644-4e21-9536-13779b8ab76f","uuid":"192b3fa7-7a14-4786-bf3b-35e89cba688b","timestamp":"2026-05-18T21:46:49.929Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"You are executing domain **m57-d2-ci-command-parity** of GSD-T milestone M57 (CI-Parity Verify Gate). Working dir: /Users/david/projects/GSD-T. Branch is already `m57-ci-parity-verify-gate` — do NOT create or switch branches. Do NOT commit (the lead commits the wave). Autonomy Level 3 — work fully autonomously, do not ask questions.\n\nCONTEXT BRIEF (grep this instead of re-walking the repo): .gsd-t/briefs/execute-m57-d2-ci-command-parity-20260518T213918Z.json\n\nRead first (in order):\n1. .gsd