erfile).\n  - Asserts: `dockerBuilt:false`, `dockerSkippedReason:'no-dockerfile'`.\n  - Separate from docker_unavailable test (Issue 3).\n\n**Issue 5 — JSON output shape shallow (key existence only):**\n- **Old assertion**: `'ok' in r`, `'detectedSource' in r`, `'commands' in r`, `'dockerBuilt' in r` — only checks **key presence**, not types or values.\n- **New assertions (342–356)**:\n  - `typeof out.ok === 'boolean'` — type assertion\n  - `out.detectedSource === 'package-scripts'` — **value** assertion\n  - `Array.isArray(out.commands)` — type assertion\n  - `typeof out.dockerBuilt === 'boolean'` — type assertion\n  - **Would FAIL** on `{ok:null, detectedSource:'', commands:null, dockerBuilt:null}` or `{ok:0, detectedSource:'default', commands:'[]', dockerBuilt:0}`.\n\n### Status Update\n\n**Appended to `.gsd-t/qa-issues.md` (2026-05-18):**\nAll 5 issues resolved with functional assertions. Unit test suite: 36/36 M57 tests PASS, 1 by-design SKIP.\n\n---\n\n**Final Verdict:** `Unit: 36/36 pass | Issues resolved: 5/5 | Still open: 0` — **PASS**"}],"totalDurationMs":164669,"totalTokens":75341,"totalToolUseCount":9,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":919,"cache_read_input_tokens":72729,"output_tokens":1689,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":919},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":4,"output_tokens":1689,"cache_read_input_tokens":72729,"cache_creation_input_tokens":919,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":919,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"toolStats":{"readCount":3,"searchCount":0,"bashCount":5,"editFileCount":1,"linesAdded":3,"linesRemoved":1,"otherToolCount":0}}}
